Text: *****Seeding will be somewhat slow, but I will continue to seed for at least a week or more. Hope you enjoy it!

One thing I forgot to mention in the description. Many of the tracks end abruptly at the point at which they are intended to loop. Editing 72 tracks to loop then fade out was a little too monumental a task for me, but maybe someone more proficient can do it.

Grrrrrrr, no track names!?!?!?

Thanks anyway :(
